Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Floral Print - Multi'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Floral Print’ delivers a lush take on the vintage canvas sneaker. Lined in breathable recycled mesh, the upper is entirely covered in a multicolor floral print that spans pink, green, lavender, coral and yellow hues. Standard Chuck Taylor elements remain intact, including contrast stitching, chrome eyelets and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. A white rubber midsole anchors the high-top silhouette.

results.name: Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Allover Metallic Stars - White'
results.story: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘Allover Metallic Stars’ updates the vintage high-top with an archival star print fashioned for big kids. Crisp white canvas is utilized on the upper, covered in orderly rows of metallic stars in a full spectrum of colors. The sneaker sits on a white rubber midsole with contrasting black pinstripes and a standard Converse All Star license plate. Midfoot eyelets offer enhanced breathability, while a SmartFOAM sockliner delivers a cushioned ride.

results.name: Wmns Gel Cumulus 23 'Pink Salt'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Pink Salt’ showcases a one-note pastel finish on a plush running shoe named after fluffy cumulus clouds. 20% recycled materials are incorporated into the engineered mesh upper, featuring reflective accents for added visibility in low-light conditions. Responsive cushioning is provided by a dual-layer FlyteFoam midsole, equipped with 3D Space Construction for a smoother ride and visible Gel technology in the heel for superior shock absorption.

Chuck Taylor All Star Superplay Sandal GS 'Unicorns'
results.story: Built for big kids, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star Superplay Sandal GS ‘Unicorns’ combines the open breathability of a sandal with the lightweight cushioning of a sneaker. Adjustable straps secure the synthetic leather upper, covered in a playful unicorn print and lined in soft textile. A webbing strap atop the tongue provides easy on and off, while a reinforced toe cap offers improved durability. The slip-on is mounted on a solid white EVA midsole for a smooth ride.

results.name: Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Embroidered Floral Print - Chambray Blue'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck 70 High ‘Embroidered Floral Print’ treats the classic silhouette to a summer-ready refresh. Organic canvas is utilized on the upper, finished in a subtle Chambray Blue color and covered in embroidered white and yellow blossoms. The high-top is mounted on a standard Chuck 70 midsole, featuring taller off-white rubber sidewalls in a glossy finish. Heritage details include a circular Chuck Taylor ankle patch and a vintage license plate affixed to the rear of the midsole.

Chuck Taylor All Star High GS 'Sunflowers - Pink'
results.story: Offered in big kid sizing, the Converse Chuck Taylor All Star High GS ‘Sunflowers’ enlivens the classic high-top with a sunny, playful aesthetic. The pink canvas upper displays a cheerful sunflower print on each side panel, depicting blossoms that appear to sprout up from the white rubber midsole. A SmartFOAM sockliner delivers enhanced comfort, while the brown rubber outsole features a traditional diamond tread for reliable traction.

Nike Air Huarache Scream Green (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Huarache ‘Scream Green’ brings back an OG colorway of Tinker Hatfield’s revolutionary running shoe in honor of its 30th anniversary. The Swoosh-free upper combines bootie-style neoprene construction in blue and fluorescent green. A midfoot overlay in white tumbled leather delivers structural support and durability, along with an exoskeletal heel cage with embossed Nike branding on the back strap. The lightweight build is mounted on a Phylon midsole with encapsulated Nike Air in the heel for enhanced cushioning with each stride.
